  "In Separate mode, this is the full API response. In Together mode, this is the extracted JSON block that was stripped from the AI's narrative response.": "En Séparé, la réponse API complète. En Ensemble, le JSON extrait.",
  "The AI writes its normal response, then appends tracker JSON at the end. ScenePulse automatically extracts and hides the JSON.": "L'IA écrit sa réponse puis ajoute le JSON. ScenePulse extrait et masque.",
  "If the AI omits the tracker payload, ScenePulse can automatically run a separate API call to recover. Requires a connection profile to be configured.": "Si l'IA omet les données, ScenePulse peut récupérer. Nécessite un profil.",
  "Dramatic": "Dramatique",
