  "None suggested yet": "Aucune suggestion",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Après la réponse, un appel silencieux génère le JSON. ~250–300s/message.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Un seul appel API — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Pas de changement de profil — pas de risque",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ L'IA a le contexte complet",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× plus rapide que Séparé",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Utilise des tokens du budget principal (~1 700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Peut réduire légèrement la longueur",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Réponses propres — pas de compétition",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Budget dédié au tracker",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Peut utiliser un profil/preset différent",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Deux appels API — 2–3× plus lent",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s de temps mort entre les appels",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ à 8 msgs — réduire à 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Le changement de profil peut causer des suppressions",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Intègre le snapshot précédent (~1.9K) sauf si = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Combien de messages récents inclure.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Mode Séparé uniquement — Ensemble utilise le contexte ST.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Le plus rapide. Pour scènes 1-à-1 (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Équilibré. Pour la plupart (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Meilleure continuité pour scènes complexes (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Contexte maximum mais plus lent et coûteux",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Plus grand facteur de vitesse. À 8 msgs ~10K — doubler double le temps. 3–4 réduit 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Mode Séparé uniquement.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Tentatives si le JSON est invalide.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Pour JSON sur GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Intègre les snapshots dans le contexte. Séparé uniquement. Le tracker reçoit toujours le précédent.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Chaque snapshot +~1.9K. 0 pour éliminer. 1 pour la continuité. Au-dessus de 1 rarement utile.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Injecté comme contexte invisible — info de référence.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Apparaît comme dit par l'utilisateur — certains modèles répondent mieux.",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "Comme sortie précédente — peut renforcer la mémoire mais confondre.",
